extends ../components/skeleton.jade

block neck
	title MadKudu | The easiest way to decrease customer churn

	script(type='text/javascript' src='js/index.js')

block body

	style.
		 p {
			font-size: 18px;
			line-height: 28px;
		}

		.heading-section {
			margin-bottom: 35px;
		}

	.wrapper
		.hero#section-signup
			.container
				h1.home-title The smartest way <br>for SaaS companies <br>to increase customer engagement
				h2.home-subtitle MadKudu analyses your customer interactions <br>and finds out how you can be most helpful and most effective.
				//- img.hero-screenshot(src='images/Accounts.png' width='80%' alt='MadKudu account dashboard')

		section.section--signup
			.container
				.signup-form-wrap#signup
					form.signup-form(id='mc-early-signup-form' name='email-form' data-name='Email Form' action='//madkudu.us8.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=50d10dbb43453c101e00a5f6f&amp;id=2562f30397' method='post')
						input.signup-field(id='mc-EMAIL' type='email' placeholder='Your email address' name='EMAIL' data-name='EMAIL' required='required')
						input.button.button-signup(type='submit' value='Send me an invite!' data-wait='Please wait...')
					.form-success
						p.signup-text Thank you! We'll get in touch very soon!
					.form-fail
						p.signup-text Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form



		section.section--explainer#section-explainer
			.container
				.row
					//- .col-md-1
					.col-md-12
						h2.heading-section Break down silos, get a complete view of your customers.
					//- .col-md-1
				.row
					//- .col-md-1
					.col-md-7.column__text
						p You already have lots of customer data. CRM, product usage, billing, marketing, support. You name it.
						p But this data is all over the place. And it is in a form that is hardly of any use to understand who your customers really are and what they care about.
						p MadKudu automatically brings all this data together. You now have a unified view of your customers, understand their journey and know how to improve it.
					.col-md-5.column__image
						img(src='images/what_customer_profile.png').image_what
					//- .col-md-1


				.row
					//- .col-md-1
					.col-md-12
						h2.heading-section.heading-section-margin-top Pro-actively reach out to customers who need attention.
					//- .col-md-1

				.row
					//- .col-md-1
					.col-md-5.column__image
						img(src='images/what_detect.png').image_what
					.col-md-7.column__text
						p Asking customers to come back after they decided to leave is like trying to convince your spouse to come back after receiving the divorce papers.
						p It is much more effective to offer to help before customers say they need attention.
						p MadKudu analyses customer interactions and find patterns that indicate a customer is having issue and need help. You can now pro-actively reach out and get those customers back on the success track.
					//- .col-md-1


				.row
					//- .col-md-1
					.col-md-12
						h2.heading-section.heading-section-margin-top Nurture each customers like if they were your only one.
					//- .col-md-1

				.row
					//- .col-md-1
					.col-md-7.column__text
						p Every customer is different. Different needs. Different stage of their journey. What works with a customer will not work with another.
						p MadKudu analyses your customer interactions and tells you the behaviors you should encourage to make your customers more engaged.
						p You can now suggest to each customers their best next step, based on what they have done and what will works best for them.
					.col-md-5.column__image
						img(src='images/what_nurture.png').image_what
					//- .col-md-1



		section.section--benefits#section-benefits
			.container
				.row
					.col-md-12.text-center
						h1(style="margin-bottom: 30px;") Meet MadKudu

				.row
					.col-md-7.column__text
						h2.heading-section &#9312; Connect
						p Turn on a few switches and get all your customer data in one place.
						p You now have visibility on the complete customer journey.
						p You can see the activity of an account or drill down to the user level.
					.col-md-5
						img(src='images/feature_integrations.png').meet_madkudu_image

				.row.heading-section-margin-top
					.col-md-5
						img(src='images/feature_detect.png' width='100%').meet_madkudu_image
					.col-md-7.column__text
						h2.heading-section &#9313; Detect
						p MadKudu's data science analyses your customer interactions to find out who needs attention, what behaviors impact engagement, and what is the best next action for each customer.


				.row.heading-section-margin-top
					.col-md-7.column__text
						h2.heading-section &#9314; Engage
						p Your customer intelligence is synced with your marketing applications or your CRM.
						p Implementing customer growth campaigns can be done simply in the applications you already use.
					.col-md-5
						img(src='images/feature_engage.png' width='100%').meet_madkudu_image


		style.
			.col-centered{
				float: none;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.column-thirty-three {
				width: 33%;
				float: left;
			}
			.column-inside-left {
				margin-left: 0px;
				margin-right: 40px;
			}
			.column-inside-center {
				margin-left: 20px;
				margin-right: 20px;
			}
			.column-inside-right {
				margin-left: 40px;
				margin-right: 0px;
			}

		section.section--why#section-why-madkudu
			.container
				.row
					.col-md-12.text-center
						h2.heading-section What's unique about MadKudu?
				.col-centered
					.row
						.column-thirty-three.text-center
							.column-inside-left
								img(src='images/why_madkudu_roi.png' width='150px')
								h2 Best ROI
								p Create amazing results without spending time and money.
						.column-thirty-three.text-center
							.column-inside-center
								img(src='images/why_madkudu_intelligent.png' width='150px')
								h2 Intelligent
								p MadKudu use advanced data science to find what matters.
						.column-thirty-three.text-center
							.column-inside-right
								img(src='images/why_madkudu_simple.png' width='150px')
								h2 Simple
								p MadKudu simplifies your life and get you results in no time.

